commit.message:
C++: fix "RT_INTERATION" typo

gcc/cp/ChangeLog:
	* parser.c (enum required_token): Fix spelling of
	RT_INTERATION to RT_ITERATION.
	(cp_parser_iteration_statement): Likewise.
	(cp_parser_required_error): Likewise.

From-SVN: r249931

+	* parser.c (enum required_token): Fix spelling of
+	RT_INTERATION to RT_ITERATION.
+	(cp_parser_iteration_statement): Likewise.
+	(cp_parser_required_error): Likewise.
